<i>noun</i>: 편견 [편견], 색안경 [새간경] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>편견 [편견]</dt><br>
<dd>prejudice; bias</dd><br>
<dd>공평하고 올바르지 못하고 한쪽으로 치우친 생각.</dd><br>
<dd>A thought that is unfair, incorrect, and one-sided.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>색안경 [새간경]</dt><br>
<dd>1. tinted glasses</dd><br>
<dd>색깔이 있는 렌즈를 끼운 안경.</dd><br>
<dd>A pair of glasses with colored lenses.</dd><br>
<dd>2. bias; prejudice</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 주관이나 선입견 때문에 좋지 않게 생각하는 태도.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) A negative attitude formed by one's own opinon or preconception.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>